songs.title: God Level
songs.lyrics:
[Produced by Kanye West, 88 Keys, Mike Dean, Noah Goldstein, and Hudson Mohawke]

[Refrain]
God level
Provide a new coffin
You don't see murder like this this often
God level
God level
Our father
Might as well make a new casket
God level
God level
God level

[Verse]
You see sharks in the water
Then they try to do nothin' but put cocks in your daughter
Don't say nothin' 'bout what Ye said
Don't move, mothafucka, play dead
Yeah, we cool, mothafucka, yeah, yeah
Yeah, yeah

[Refrain]
God level
